<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>ThirstAlert Password Reset</title>
  <style>
    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
      background-color: #191A1F;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
    .button {
      background-color: #0D6766;
      color: #FFFFFF;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <img src="https://storage.googleapis.com/thirst-alert-public-assets/thirst-alert-assets/logo.png"/>
    <p>Hey {{username}}! We just received a request to reset your password for your ThirstAlert account. Click the button below to reset your password:</p>
    <a href="{{reset_url}}" class="button">Reset Password</a>
    <p>Please not that this link expires in one hour for security purposes.</p>
    <p>If you didn't request a password reset, you can safely ignore this email.</p>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>Best regards,<br>The ThirstAlert Team</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
